snippet.title: 【FINAL FANTASY IX】Trailer　SP & PC
snippet.description:
Selling over five million copies since its release
in 2000, FINAL FANTASY IX proudly returns on smartphones 
and PC! Now you can relive the adventures of
Zidane and his crew in the palm of your hands!

http://www.jp.square-enix.com/ff9/en/
